0154|- [HelpText]
0155|*In typical statistical operations (like LINREG and FACTA) the maximum
0156|*number of variables in SURVO 84C was at most 90.
0157|*In SURVO MM greatest permitted dimensions are much higher but depend
0158|*on the size of the central memory. In 128MB no substantial limits
0159|*will be encountered. For example, factor analysis can be made even
0160|*with 1000 variables.
